text: The apartment is exactly as described.  Great location (a couple blocks from 290, 15 minutes from the airport) and easy to find.  It's well furnished and clean with everything you need for a comfortable stay.  Courtney also provides a list of restaurants, shop & bars in the area, which there are quite a few.  Thanks again, great stay!
title: Cozy Treehouse Apt with 2 Bikes
